node.text: Who knew max had a lizard farm?? 😂😂 anywho... who wants one of these babies?!? They will be ready at the end of this week for a new home. They are eastern collars and soo easy to take care of.

Gunner wanted a spinach feta wrap from Starbucks for breakfast 😂 so to Abilene we went. Hit up the splash pad and did our HEB curbside ♥️💙 these kiddos make my world go round 🌎 I’m so lucky they are mine.
Your wild heart does my soul good 💗
Thank you @rae.b.730  for having us at your church today. Gunner had such a great time and cannot wait to go back. 💙
💗 One day closer. It’s been a long month. One more to go.
To the one we get to call our own. Ever giving, loving, teaching. 💕 we struck gold with him and I’ll be thankful for it everyday.
...when a fruit/veggie buffet makes your heart so happy ♥️🤓 yumm
When everyone thinks they need scratches at the same time. Moochers 😂🥰🤦🏻‍♀️
Yay!!! Bubba did so good at the track meet today!! His little cheerleader was pretty adorable too.
Look how much they have grown. From their first to one of their last days of school. Man 😍🥰
We had a great anniversary weekend. 😍 date night, crawfish boil, tons of family and fun. ♥️
Gunner loved this puzzle, getting to talk about all the places we have been and where he’d like to go. ❤️💙
When you go out of town for a day and everyone misses the big man on campus 💙 he did a celebratory HEEEEE when we got home
My girls are enjoying this mild weather 🌤🌈
